BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
10
11
SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
11
12
in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 230.19 of Title 47, unless there
12
13
is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
13
14
During an Oklahoma Motor Carrier Safety and Hazardous Materials
14
15
Transportation Act administrative hearing, a motor carrier organized
15
16
as a corporation, limited liability company, limited liability
16
17
partnership, or partnership may be represented by an officer,
17
18
member, manager, or partner of the entity at the administrative
18
19
hearing if the motor carrier chooses not to be represented by an
19
20
attorney.
20
21
SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
